Spider Man PC Gameplay | Spider-Man PC 4K Gameplay | Spider Man PC Walkthrough | PC 4K 60FPS | Remastered |

Spider-Man (Marvel's) is a 2018 open-world action-adventure game developed by Insomniac Games and published by Sony Interactive Entertainment. Set in the borough of Manhattan in a fictionalized version of modern-day New York City and based on the Marvel Comics character Spider-Man, In the main story, the super-human crime lord Mister Negative orchestrates a plot to seize control of New York City's criminal underworld. released for the PlayStation 4 on September 7, 2018, and a remastered version of Spider-Man for the PlayStation 5 and Windows August 12, 2022. A sequel, Marvel's Spider-Man 2, is scheduled for release in 2023.
